  "keyFeatures": [
    "Incremental backup using manifests — only new and changed files are copied",
    "Quick hash (header+tail 64 KB) for fast change detection without full file reads",
    "Adaptive copy concurrency based on detected drive type (SSD / HDD / USB)",
    "Content-level deduplication via NTFS hardlinks and a content-index",
    "Optional versioning: previous revisions of changed files compressed with gzip",
    "Optional deep verification with full SHA-256 checksums",
    "Operation journal: detects interrupted backups and cleans up partial files",
    "Compare tab: finds files missing from the PC and restores only those",
    "Restore tab: full folder restore to any location, without needing the original path",
    "Automatic name disambiguation for source folders sharing the same base name",
    "Light/dark theme with persistent preference",
    "Configurable exclusion filters (Thumbs.db, node_modules, *.tmp, etc.)",
    "Secure Electron architecture: contextIsolation, no nodeIntegration, path traversal protection"
  ],
